    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. This example is mechanically robust, benefiting from a recent VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement\u2014essential for maintaining the structural integrity of this chassis. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory variable M-differential. The suspension remains tight, utilizing its original geometry to provide the communicative steering feedback these cars are famed for. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, its performance remains uncompromised, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
